  "title": "AfterViewInit",
  "contents": "\n\n<article>\n  <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/core/src/metadata/lifecycle_hooks.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L183-L210\" aria-label=\"Suggest Edits\" title=\"Suggest Edits\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/6.1.0/packages/core/src/metadata/lifecycle_hooks.ts#L183-L210\" aria-label=\"View Source\" title=\"View Source\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n    <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n      {\n        \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n        \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n        \"itemListElement\": [\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io//api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/core\", \"name\": \"@angular/core\" } },\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/core/AfterViewInit\", \"name\": \"AfterViewInit\" } }\n        ]\n      }\n    </script>\n      <a href=\"/api\">API</a> / <a href=\"api/core\">@angular/core</a>\n  </div>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"afterviewinit\">AfterViewInit<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/AfterViewInit#afterviewinit\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label interface\">interface</label>\n    \n    \n    <label class=\"api-status-label stable\">stable</label>\n    \n  </header>\n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n    \n  <p class=\"short-description\"></p><p translation-origin=\"off\">A lifecycle hook that is called after Angular has fully initialized\na component's view.\nDefine an <code>ngAfterViewInit()</code> method to handle any additional initialization tasks.</p>\n<p></p>\n  \n  \n  <section class=\"interface-overview\">\n<code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\">\ninterface <a href=\"api/core/AfterViewInit\" class=\"code-anchor\">AfterViewInit</a> {\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/core/AfterViewInit#ngAfterViewInit\">ngAfterViewInit(): void</a>\n}\n</code-example>\n\n  \n  \n\n\n  \n  \n\n</section>\n  \n<section class=\"see-also\">\n  <h2 id=\"see-also\">See also<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/AfterViewInit#see-also\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <ul>\n  \n    <li><p translation-origin=\"off\"><code><a href=\"api/core/OnInit\" class=\"code-anchor\">OnInit</a></code></p>\n</li>\n    <li><p translation-origin=\"off\"><code><a href=\"api/core/AfterContentInit\" class=\"code-anchor\">AfterContentInit</a></code></p>\n</li>\n    <li><p translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/lifecycle-hooks#onchanges\">Lifecycle Hooks</a> guide</p>\n</li>\n  </ul>\n</section>\n\n\n  \n  \n  \n\n\n  \n\n<section class=\"instance-methods\">\n  <h2 id=\"methods\">Methods<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/AfterViewInit#methods\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  \n    <a id=\"ngAfterViewInit\"></a>\n<table class=\"is-full-width method-table instance-method\">\n  <thead><tr><th>\n    <div class=\"with-github-links\">\n      <h3 id=\"ngafterviewinit\">\n        ngAfterViewInit()\n        \n      <a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/AfterViewInit#ngafterviewinit\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n      <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/core/src/metadata/lifecycle_hooks.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L203-L209\" aria-label=\"Suggest Edits\" title=\"Suggest Edits\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/6.1.0/packages/core/src/metadata/lifecycle_hooks.ts#L203-L209\" aria-label=\"View Source\" title=\"View Source\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n    </div>\n  </th></tr></thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td class=\"short-description\">\n        <p translation-origin=\"off\">A callback method that is invoked immediately after\nAngular has completed initialization of a component's view.\nIt is invoked only once when the view is instantiated.</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr>\n      <td>\n        \n\n<code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" linenums=\"false\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">ngAfterViewInit(): void</code-example>\n\n<h4 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"parameters\">Parameters</h4>\n<p>There are no parameters.</p>\n\n\n<h4 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"returns\">Returns</h4>\n<p translation-origin=\"off\"><code>void</code></p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n\n  \n\n  \n    </tbody>\n</table>\n\n  \n</section>\n\n\n  \n<section class=\"usage-notes\">\n  <h2 id=\"usage-notes\">Usage notes<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/AfterViewInit#usage-notes\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p translation-origin=\"off\">The following snippet shows how a component can implement this interface to\ndefine its own view initialization method.</p>\n<code-example>\n@<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a>({selector: 'my-cmp', <a href=\"api/core/Component#template\" class=\"code-anchor\">template</a>: `...`})\nclass MyComponent implements <a href=\"api/core/AfterViewInit\" class=\"code-anchor\">AfterViewInit</a> {\n  ngAfterViewInit() {\n    // ...\n  }\n}\n\n</code-example>\n\n</section>\n\n\n\n  </div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/core\n - api/core/AfterContentInit\n - api/core/ViewChild\n - api/core/ViewChildren\n - api/forms/NgForm\n - guide/component-interaction\n - guide/lifecycle-hooks\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/core\n - api/core/AfterContentInit\n - api/core/AfterViewInit#afterviewinit\n - api/core/AfterViewInit#methods\n - api/core/AfterViewInit#ngAfterViewInit\n - api/core/AfterViewInit#ngafterviewinit\n - api/core/AfterViewInit#see-also\n - api/core/AfterViewInit#usage-notes\n - api/core/Component\n - api/core/Component#template\n - api/core/OnInit\n - guide/lifecycle-hooks#onchanges\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/core/src/metadata/lifecycle_hooks.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L183-L210\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/core/src/metadata/lifecycle_hooks.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L203-L209\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/6.1.0/packages/core/src/metadata/lifecycle_hooks.ts#L183-L210\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/6.1.0/packages/core/src/metadata/lifecycle_hooks.ts#L203-L209\n-->"
